st forgot...The nightclub is full of prostitutes that look as if they may be teenagers....we thought it was tasteless for an upscale nightclub to allow this sort of thing. (and yeah...they know)....but I guess that's why some people go to Vegas. Great hotel for a bunch of bachelors but not so great for a couple or family.	
