 check out the views from Stratosphere and the food at Seredipity 3, and Moos (big guy working at the tour desk) at CVS will sort you out good prices for day trips to Grand Canyon etc as well as free club entry.Book online for best prices in advance. Only bad thing - no WIFI. Its $13 a day. ouch.	
