parently entitled us to 2 bottles of water and a newspaper each day. I have no problem paying this fee, but expext to receive the promised items, most days we were left 1 bottle of water, and it was hit and miss if your paper was outside in the morning. After having a good look around the other strip hotels, I feel that there were much better hotels within the same price range or within £100 or so either way. We will definitely be returning, but will stay elsewhere. I am not one to moan for the sake of it, just my personal opinion. We chose PH as it seemed to be getting good reviews at the time of booking, with the benefit of experience and seeing the other hotels, I will not choose this hotel again.	
